{"tid":767132,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"一到夏天就暴瘦的Red Velvet Wendy！臨近回歸，重回巔峰","createTime":"2018-08-04T08:32:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T14:17:12.000Z","uid":74065,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f6db9c1262a41baafd99107fc77532471d7be1e9","tid":767132,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T08:32:43.000Z","msg":"希望Wendy不再是氣球人~<br />\n<br />\n去年夏天《Red Flavor》打歌的時候，Wendy瘦到能見到肋骨，令粉絲擔憂她的身體健康。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_94fbffdb3c00b7a562c2a3393bd054c6/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-08-02/108023-640943.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_94fbffdb3c00b7a562c2a3393bd054c6%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2018-08-02%2F108023-640943.jpg&h=e77168b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n過後Wendy又發福了，能看出來三四月的Wendy明顯肉肉的。 在今年5月底到6月底，Wendy用一個月的時間就瘦回來了！ 看來那個月對自己下了狠心，最近為了回歸，更是瘦回完美身材。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_b8ded9c5e6a6fa06a17a7630ecdcc1cd/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-08-02/108023-640942.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_b8ded9c5e6a6fa06a17a7630ecdcc1cd%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2018-08-02%2F108023-640942.jpg&h=a27eed04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_3b11933eeaf8b25c18520160cf8eb2f3/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-08-02/108023-640945.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_3b11933eeaf8b25c18520160cf8eb2f3%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2018-08-02%2F108023-640945.jpg&h=4324165d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"489aca224fddc26a927200e388a7ee962006ac44","tid":767132,"uid":3405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"